      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Why Version Control Exists",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Version control didn‚Äôt appear because developers love tools.",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "text": "It appeared because ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "everything kept breaking",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ".",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Early software development had one brutal problem:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Multiple people working on the same code with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "no reliable way to track changes",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "No history.",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "text": "No accountability.",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "text": "No undo button.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Version control exists to answer three simple questions:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Who changed this?",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "What exactly changed?",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "How do we go back if this breaks?",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Without version control, the answer was usually:",
          "type": "text"
        }
